26
00:03:43,846 --> 00:03:46,140
Zato sam se vratila i kupila ti.

27
00:03:46,265 --> 00:03:49,018
Nensi, dušo, dodaj mi moju torbicu.

28
00:03:49,102 --> 00:03:52,856
Zašto uvek mene gnjavite da donesem torbicu?

29
00:03:52,940 --> 00:03:55,693
Najmladja Griffith devojka je boginja torbica.

30
00:03:55,776 --> 00:03:56,236
Oh, bako.

31
00:03:56,361 --> 00:03:57,696
Otvori moje.

32
00:03:57,863 --> 00:04:00,449
Zašto ja moram biti sluga za torbice?

33
00:04:00,532 --> 00:04:01,284
Ok. Dobro.

34
00:04:05,079 --> 00:04:06,623
Da, mislim da mi pristaje.

35
00:04:06,707 --> 00:04:08,292
Šta vi mislite?

36
00:04:08,375 --> 00:04:10,878
Bako, to ti je božanstvena nijansa ruža za usne.

37
00:04:11,003 --> 00:04:11,503
Prelepo!

38
00:04:12,213 --> 00:04:13,340
Oh, Ed, prestani.

39
00:04:13,423 --> 00:04:15,050
Zašto? Šta nije uredu, mama?

40
00:04:15,175 --> 00:04:15,925
Odvratno je.

41
00:04:17,052 --> 00:04:18,011
Ako pitaš mene,

42
00:04:18,095 --> 00:04:21,599
